# Employee Management System (Django CRUD)

A simple Employee Management System built using Django.
This project demonstrates basic CRUD operations (Create, Read, Update, Delete) for managing employee records.

## Features

* Add new employee
* View employee list
* Update employee details
* Delete employee
* Simple UI using HTML and CSS

## Technologies Used

* Python
* Django
* HTML
* CSS
* SQLite Database

